description: A spelling of the letter f (also spelled ef), the initial letter of the vulgar term fuck. Compare pee.

verbs.description: eff (third-person singular simple present effs, present participle effing, simple past and past participle effed)

entries.meaning: (euphemistic, slang) Fuck (the taboo swear word, but not in the sense "to copulate")
examples: And he kept saying, "Effing this, effing that."

verbs.description: eff (third-person singular simple present effs, present participle effing, simple past and past participle effed)

entries.meaning: To put into words; to express.
